Day 3
Ensure you are in the linux directory by typing pwd, else cd into linux directory
Create 3 files using the touch comand namely Day 3, testfile1 and testfile2 respectively
Create a directory called Demo
Run the ls -l command to list the files and folder
move testfile1 into the Demo directory using the mv command
Copy Day3 file into the Demo directory using the cp command
cd into the Demo directory and run the ls -l command to comfirm the files existsin the location
Go back into the linux directory and delete the Demo directory with it's file content sing the rm -rf command
Delete testfile2 using the rm command
vi into Day3 file and using the insert command input all these instruction (use copy and paste)
